<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">THE GIRL WITH NO SHADOW is the US title of THE LOLLIPOP SHOES. It wasn&apos;t my decision to publish it under a different name, but that of the US publishe<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">THE GIRL WITH NO SHADOW is the US title of THE LOLLIPOP SHOES. It wasn't my decision to publish it under a different name, but that of the US publisher.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
