<a href="/questions/853780-is-it-important-to-read-chocolat-first-i">Is it important to read Chocolat first? I have seen the movie, but wondering if it&#39;s needed for this book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_853780'><a id="like_count_community_question_853780" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/853780?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2227371.The_Girl_with_No_Shadow">like</a></span>

